    <item>
      <title>普京转向技术官僚来启动俄罗斯的战争机器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/putin-turns-to-a-technocrat-to-crank-up-russia-s-war-machine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗拉基米尔·普京总统在深夜出人意料地对国防和安全团队进行了调整，这表明他决心调动俄罗斯的战时经济来应对乌克兰与西方的长期激烈冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/putin-turns-to-a-technocrat-to-crank-up-russia-s-war-machine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 07:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中韩高级外交官将在北京举行罕见会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/top-china-south-korea-diplomats-set-for-rare-talks-in-beijing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国和中国高级外交官将在北京举行六年来的首次会谈，美国的半导体出口政策和朝鲜的核野心可能会主导此次会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/top-china-south-korea-diplomats-set-for-rare-talks-in-beijing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 06:26:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑德斯敦促丹麦向诺和诺德施压，要求其降低药品价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/sanders-urges-denmark-to-pressure-novo-nordisk-on-drug-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员伯尼·桑德斯在致北欧国家最大报纸之一的一封信中敦促丹麦迫使其最有价值的公司诺和诺德公司降低药品价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/sanders-urges-denmark-to-pressure-novo-nordisk-on-drug-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 06:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管塞浦路斯紧张局势持续，土耳其和希腊仍致力于改善关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/turkey-and-greece-aim-to-better-ties-even-as-cyprus-tensions-linger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯将于周一在安卡拉会见土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安，北约东南侧邻国致力于改善长期紧张的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/turkey-and-greece-aim-to-better-ties-even-as-cyprus-tensions-linger</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非种族隔离后最激烈的选举中的名人录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/who-s-who-in-south-africa-s-tightest-post-apartheid-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自三十年前白人少数统治结束以来，南非首次进入全国选举，而选举中没有明显的获胜者。一系列民意调查显示，执政的非洲人国民大会有可能在 5 月 29 日的投票中失去多数席位，可能必须争取一个或多个竞争对手的支持才能继续治理非洲工业化程度最高的经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/who-s-who-in-south-africa-s-tightest-post-apartheid-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克什米尔即将举行投票，印度得票率已过半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/india-election-crosses-halfway-mark-with-focus-on-low-turnout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[位于动荡的查谟和克什米尔地区的一座城市斯利那加周一在印度第四阶段全国选举中进行了投票，人们对选民投票率低下和竞选活动日益激烈的担忧日益加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/india-election-crosses-halfway-mark-with-focus-on-low-turnout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑙塞达准备晋级立陶宛总统选举决选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/nauseda-poised-to-advance-to-lithuania-s-presidential-election-run-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛总统吉塔纳斯·瑙塞达周日赢得了第一轮选举，这使得这位直言不讳地批评俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的人更接近获得连任国家元首的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/nauseda-poised-to-advance-to-lithuania-s-presidential-election-run-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 22:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>社会主义者赢得加泰罗尼亚选票，但该地区陷入僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/socialist-election-win-in-catalonia-may-upend-spain-s-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯领导的社会党首次赢得加泰罗尼亚地方选举，这显然证明了他对非法独立公投给予分离主义者特赦的策略是正确的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/socialist-election-win-in-catalonia-may-upend-spain-s-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 21:34:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
